---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Contact | Free Estimates"
description: "Call or text CNO Pole Barns at (248) 625-2334 for a free estimate, or email zosim@cnopolebarns.com. Serving Oakland, Genesee, Lapeer, and Macomb counties from Clarkston, Michigan."
image: "/images/projects/pole-barn-truss-crew.jpg"
permalink: /contact/
---

{% set crumbs = [{name:"Home",url:"/"},{name:"Contact",url:"/contact/"}] %}
{% set faq = [
  {q:"How fast will I hear back?", a:"Zosim answers most calls himself. If he's on a roof or with another customer, leave a message or send the form and he'll call back."},
  {q:"Is the estimate really free?", a:"Yes. We come look at your site and give you a straightforward price. No obligation to book anything."},
  {q:"I don't know the exact size I need. Can I still call?", a:"Yes. Tell us roughly what you're picturing and we'll help you land on the right size when we walk the site."},
  {q:"Will the price change once you start building?", a:"We agree on a contract up front and stick to those numbers unless you approve a change. No surprise add-ons at the end."},
  {q:"Do you serve my area?", a:"We build across Oakland, Genesee, Lapeer, and Macomb counties from our base in Clarkston. Call and ask if you're not sure you're in range."}
] %}

{# ===== overlay hero (solid band, no stock photo) ===== #}
<header class="ohero noimg">
  <div class="wrap"><div class="ohero-inner stagger">
    <div class="crumbs">{% for c in crumbs %}{% if not loop.last %}<a href="{{ c.url }}">{{ c.name }}</a> <span>/</span> {% else %}<span>{{ c.name }}</span>{% endif %}{% endfor %}</div>
    <span class="lab">Talk to a builder, not a call center</span>
    <h1>Get A Free Estimate</h1>
    <p class="lead">Call, text, or send the form below. Zosim answers directly and gives you a straight answer about cost and timeline, not a sales script.</p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a class="btn btn-gold" href="tel:{{ site.phoneTel }}">Call {{ site.phone }}</a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">Email {{ site.email }}</a>
    </div>
  </div></div>
</header>

{# ===== direct lines ===== #}
<section class="blk">
  <div class="wrap coverage">
    <div>
      <div class="lab reveal" style="margin-bottom:20px">Direct lines</div>
      <h2 class="reveal">Call, Text, Or Email</h2>
      <p class="lede reveal">Every call and message goes to Zosim directly. If he's on a roof when you call, he'll call you back.</p>
      <p class="lede reveal">Prefer email? Write to <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}" style="color:var(--pine);border-bottom:1px solid var(--gold)">{{ site.email }}</a> and attach a few photos of your site if you have them.</p>
      <p class="lede reveal">We build across Oakland, Genesee, Lapeer, and Macomb counties from our base in Clarkston. See the full <a href="/areas/" style="color:var(--pine);border-bottom:1px solid var(--gold)">service area</a>.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hours-card riv">
      <h3>Hours</h3>
      <div class="row"><span>Monday - Saturday</span><b>8:30 AM - 7:00 PM</b></div>
      <div class="row"><span>Sunday</span><b>Closed</b></div>
      <a class="ph" href="tel:{{ site.phoneTel }}">{{ site.phone }}</a>
      <p class="note">Zosim picks up. If he's on a roof, he calls back.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ===== estimate form + sidebar ===== #}
<div class="artwrap">
  <article class="article reveal">
    <h2>Tell Us What You're Building</h2>
    <p>Fill this out with a few details and Zosim will follow up. No obligation, no pressure.</p>

    <form class="form" action="https://formsubmit.co/{{ site.email }}" method="POST">
      <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="Estimate request from cnopolebarns.com">
      <div class="frow">
        <label>Name
          <input type="text" name="name" required placeholder="Your name">
        </label>
        <label>Phone
          <input type="tel" name="phone" required placeholder="(248) 555-1234">
        </label>
      </div>
      <div class="frow">
        <label>Town
          <input type="text" name="town" placeholder="Clarkston, MI">
        </label>
        <label>What are you building?
          <select name="project_type">
            <option value="">Select one</option>
            <option value="Pole barn">Pole barn</option>
            <option value="Garage">Garage</option>
            <option value="Horse barn">Horse barn</option>
            <option value="Barndominium">Barndominium</option>
            <option value="Steel building">Steel building</option>
            <option value="Roofing">Roofing</option>
            <option value="Something else">Something else</option>
          </select>
        </label>
      </div>
      <label>Message
        <textarea name="message" rows="5" placeholder="Rough size, timeline, anything else we should know."></textarea>
      </label>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-gold">Send estimate request</button>
    </form>

    <h2>Common Questions</h2>
    <div class="faqwrap stagger">
      {% for item in faq %}
      <div class="faq"><div class="faq-q">{{ item.q }}</div><div class="faq-a"><p>{{ item.a }}</p></div></div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </article>

  <aside class="aside">
    <div class="scard">
      <h4>What to have ready</h4>
      <p>Three things make for a faster, more accurate estimate.</p>
      <ul class="badges">
        <li><svg width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> A few photos of the site</li>
        <li><svg width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> A rough size in mind</li>
        <li><svg width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> A rough timeline</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="scard">
      <h4>Why CNO</h4>
      <ul class="badges">
        <li><svg width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> A+ BBB Rated</li>
        <li><svg width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Licensed &amp; Insured</li>
        <li><svg width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Certified Federal Steel Builder</li>
        <li><svg width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Building since 1970</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </aside>
</div>

{# ===== cta ===== #}
<section class="blk cta"><div class="wrap"><div class="box reveal">
  <div>
    <h2>Rather Just Call?</h2>
    <p>Skip the form. Call the number below and Zosim will pick up, or leave a message and he'll call back.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <a class="btn btn-gold" href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">Email instead</a>
    <span class="or">or call</span>
    <a class="bigph" href="tel:{{ site.phoneTel }}">{{ site.phone }}</a>
  </div>
</div></div></section>

{# ===== json-ld: breadcrumb ===== #}
{% include "partials/schema-breadcrumb.njk" %}

{# ===== json-ld: faqpage ===== #}
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    {% for item in faq %}{
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": {{ item.q | dump | safe }},
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": {{ item.a | dump | safe }}
      }
    }{% if not loop.last %},{% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  ]
}
</script>
